videos.description: Baylor guard Davion Mitchell tries to drop in a layup, but Kansas center Udoka Azuibuke rises up to swat the shot off the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kansas' Azubuike blocks shot off the backboard) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kansas' Azubuike blocks shot off the backboard

videos.description: Baylor guard Jared Butler drives around a screen, pulls up from beyond the arc and knocks down the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baylor's Butler uses screen perfectly for 3-pointer) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Butler uses screen perfectly for 3-pointer

videos.description: Kansas center Udoka Azubuike throws down a big dunk, and Baylor guard Matthew Mayer answers back with a 3-pointer on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mayer answers Azubuike's dunk with a 3-pointer) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mayer answers Azubuike's dunk with a 3-pointer

videos.description: Baylor guard Davion Mitchell lobs the ball up to guard Mark Vital, who finishes with a huge two-handed jam while drawing a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baylor's Vital emphatically throws down and-1 alley-oop) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Vital emphatically throws down and-1 alley-oop

videos.description: Kansas center Udoka Azubuike pump-fakes to shake off a defender and then throws down a two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kansas' Azubuike fakes out defender for the dunk) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kansas' Azubuike fakes out defender for the dunk

videos.description: Kansas guard Devon Dotson tosses the ball up to center Udoka Azubuike, who throws down a two-handed jam over Baylor forward Freddie Gillespie.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Azubuike throws down dunk over defender) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Azubuike throws down dunk over defender

videos.description: Kansas guard Marcus Garrett sends the ball up to Udoka Azubuike, who finishes with the two-handed flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kansas' Garrett feeds Azubuike for the jam) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kansas' Garrett feeds Azubuike for the jam

videos.description: Baylor forward Freddie Gillespie tries to put up a jumper, but Kansas center Udoka Azubuike jumps high to swat the shot away.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gillespie's jumper denied by Azubuike) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gillespie's jumper denied by Azubuike

videos.description: Baylor guard Jared Butler sends the ball up to guard Mark Vital for a two-handed dunk that gets the Bears' fans to their feet.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Butler's alley-oop to Vital gets Baylor crowd going) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler's alley-oop to Vital gets Baylor crowd going

videos.description: Baylor guard MaCio Teague knocks down a 3-pointer with 16.2 seconds left to bring the Bears within one point of Kansas at 62-61.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Teague's 3-pointer makes things interesting for Bayor) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Teague's 3-pointer makes things interesting for Bayor

videos.description: Baylor guard Jared Butler tries to knock down a game-tying 3-pointer at the buzzer, but he can't get it to drop as Kansas holds on to win.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Butler can't hit game-tying 3-pointer at the buzzer) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler can't hit game-tying 3-pointer at the buzzer
